@startuml
title 会话记忆机制 - Session Memory Flow

actor "用户" as User
participant "ChatController\n/api/chat/q" as Ctrl
participant "DeepseekChatClient" as Deepseek
participant "MessageChatMemoryAdvisor" as Advisor
database "Redis ChatMemory\nkey = default" as Redis
participant "DeepSeek LLM" as LLM

== 第1轮对话：用户发问 ==

User -> Ctrl : GET /api/chat/q?question=你好
Ctrl -> Deepseek : q("你好")

Deepseek -> Advisor : before()
note right
  advisor.before(prompt):
  从 Redis 加载历史消息
  拼接到 System Prompt 之后
end note
Advisor -> Redis : get("default")
Redis --> Advisor : [] (空列表，无历史)
Advisor --> Deepseek : prompt = [sys + "你好"]

Deepseek -> LLM : call model(prompt)
LLM --> Deepseek : "你好！很高兴为你服务..."

Deepseek -> Advisor : after(response)
note right
  advisor.after(response):
  将本轮对话写入 Redis
  [userMsg("你好"), assistantMsg("...")]
end note
Advisor -> Redis : add("default", [userMsg, assistantMsg])
Advisor --> Deepseek : ok

Deepseek --> Ctrl : "你好！很高兴为你服务..."
Ctrl --> User : 200 OK

== 第2轮对话：用户询问历史 ==

User -> Ctrl : GET /api/chat/q?question=我刚刚问你的是什么
Ctrl -> Deepseek : q("我刚刚问你的是什么")

Deepseek -> Advisor : before()
Advisor -> Redis : get("default")
Redis --> Advisor : ["你好", "你好！很高兴为你..."]
note right
  历史消息已存在！
  包含上一轮的 USER + ASSISTANT 消息
end note
Advisor --> Deepseek : prompt = [sys + "你好" + "你好！很高兴为你..." + "我刚刚问你的是什么"]

Deepseek -> LLM : call model(prompt)
LLM --> Deepseek : "你刚刚问的是：'你好'..."

Deepseek -> Advisor : after(response)
Advisor -> Redis : add("default", [userMsg, assistantMsg])
Advisor --> Deepseek : ok

Deepseek --> Ctrl : "你刚刚问的是：'你好'..."
Ctrl --> User : 200 OK

== 问题场景：多用户并发 ==

User -> Ctrl : GET /api/chat/q?question=... (用户B)
note over Deepseek
  用户B的请求也使用 conversationId = "default"
  与用户A读写同一条 Redis List
  用户B的请求会带上用户A的历史消息
  会话数据互相污染！
end note

note right of Redis
  Redis 存储结构：
  key:  "default"
  type: List
  len:  168 条消息
  
  内容截取:
  [USER] "你好"
  [ASSISTANT] "你好！很高兴..."
  [USER] "今天天气怎么样"
  ...
end note

@enduml
